<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <link rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.googleapis.com' />
    <link
      rel='stylesheet'
      href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap'
    />
    <style>
      @font-face {
        font-family: 'Roboto';
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: 400;
        src: url('https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/roboto/v18/KFOmCnqEu92Fr1Mu7WxKOzY.woff2')
          format('woff2');
      }
      body {
        background-color: #e3e3e3;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif !important;
      }
      .main-wrapper {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
        padding: 42px 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 35px 25px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 4px solid #1fac58;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 25px;
        background: transparent;
        border: 2px solid #03AC4F;
        border-radius: 40px;
        color: #505050;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #84828e;
        background-color: #f2eff3;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='main-wrapper'>
      <div class='container'>
        <img src='{{logoUrl}}' alt='Logo' width='60' height='39' />
        <h1
          style="font-family:'Roboto','Helvetica Neue',Segoe UI,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight: 600;color: #111; font-size: 24px;line-height: 28px;word-spacing: 0px;"
        >Please get your code ðŸ˜€</h1>
        <p
          style="font-family:'Roboto','Helvetica Neue',Segoe UI,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight: 500;color: #424040;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: -0.6px;word-spacing: 0px;line-height: 22px;"
        >The code is valid for
          <span
            style="font-family:'Roboto','Helvetica Neue',Segoe UI,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight: 500;color: #EC1E26;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: -0.6px;word-spacing: 0px;line-height: 22px;"
          >5 minute.</span>
          Please do not share this code with anyone.</p>
        <div class='cta-button'>{{code}}</div>
        <p
          style="font-family:'Roboto','Helvetica Neue',Segoe UI,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;margin-top: 20px; font-size: 15px;font-weight: 500;color: #424040;letter-spacing: -0.6px;word-spacing: 0px;line-height: 22px;"
        >
          You're receiving this email because you have an account in Skipli. If you
          are not sure why you're receiving this, please contact us by replying
          to this email.
        </p>
        <div
          class='footer'
          style="font-family:'Roboto','Helvetica Neue',Segoe UI,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;font-weight: 500;"
        >
          <p>
            <em
              style="font-family:'Roboto','Helvetica Neue',Segoe UI,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"
            >Socialize with us</em>
            on
            <a
              href='https://facebook.com/{{facebookPage}}'
              target='_blank'
            >Facebook</a>
            |
            <a
              href='https://www.youtube.com/channel/{{youtubeHandle}}'
              target='_blank'
            >Youtube</a>
            |
            <a
              href='https://www.pinterest.com/{{pinterestHandle}}'
              target='_blank'
            >Pinterest</a>
            |
            <a
              href='https://www.linkedin.com/company/{{linkedinHandle}}'
              target='_blank'
            >Linkedin</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>M:</strong>
            {{supportPhone}}
            |
            <strong>E:</strong>
            <a
              href='https://mail.google.com/mail/?view=cm&fs=1&to={{supportEmail}}'
            >{{supportEmail}}</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>